      "content": "that's exactly what i was thinking... it feels intentional. like it was meant to be forgotten. i also found these old, handwritten letters between my great-grandfather and someone named 'General K'. the letters talk about \"the weight of the crown\" and \"protecting the lineage until the sun rises again.\" it's so cryptic. do you think there's any historical precedent for a royal line being forced into hiding like that? like maybe they were deposed and had to go underground?",
