      "content": "it's just so eerie to read. like, \"protecting the lineage\" isn't something you say in a normal letter. and the way the ring looks, it's not just a crest, it's like a symbol of authority. if this was a real royal line that got wiped from the books, how would they even do that? like, how could an entire dynasty just... vanish from history without leaving a trace in the major records? it makes me wonder if my whole family history has been a lie to keep us safe.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
